GENERAL SERVICE KNOWLEDGE (SD/SW)
CHAPTER III : MODERNIZATION OF IAF (MOAF)
TEACHING INSTRUCTIONS
Period:03 (Three)
Type:Lecture
Year:1st Yr SD/SW
Conducting Officer:Permanent Instructor
Training Aids:Classroom, OHP, Board, Screen, Pointer,
Marker, Book Flagged, or Lesson Plan, File
and Aircraft Model.
Time Plan
